{
  "texts": [
    "All animals were perfused once every other day for three consecutive days.",
    "Twelve hours after the last perfusion, samples were collected for evaluation of VDS, %PMN, coagulation and ATP concentration.",
    "ATP contents in whole blood were detected with an ATP assay kit (Beyotime Biotechnology, Shanghai, China).",
    "Whole blood was lysed using the lysis buffer provided in the kit.",
    "After lysis, the samples were centrifuged at 12,000 g for 10 min at 4 °C."
  ]
}